author: mfreedman
msg: Fixes PORTLETBRIDGE-54, PORTLETBRIDGE-51, PORTLETBRIDGE-50, PORTLETBRIDGE-49, PORTLETBRIDGE-47, PORTLETBRIDGE-45, PORTLETBRIDGE-44, PORTLETBRIDGE-43, PORTLETBRIDGE-42, PORTLETBRIDGE-41, PORTLETBRIDGE-40, PORTLETBRIDGE-38, PORTLETBRIDGE-37

This commit brings the Portlet 2.0 Bridge branch up to date with respect to Portlet 1.0 Bridge.  I.e. I have merged all applicable changes that have occurred since last April (2008).  This checkin includes the latest support for in protocol resources and public render parameters.  Events support isn't implemented yet nor is using forward to dispatch to JSPs as Pluto has a bug preventing the use of forward.
